metadata.name: #2/50 Diamond Jersey - Rough Diamonds
metadata.description: With only 50 created, this is the most exclusive Fan Jersey in the Rough Diamonds universe. In addition to gaining priority in all future NFT drops, Diamonds Jersey holders will be a part of key decisions regarding next year's Rough Diamonds squad selection and have other perks related to physical/digital merchandise releases and other creative collaborations. We are creating a new immersive sports experience. Made for fans. By fans. https://roughdiamonds.io/
